## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **CCTV Feed**: Should the CCTV URL be a live video stream (RTSP/HLS), a static image URL, or a webcam feed? For the MVP, I'll use an image/video URL that the admin can paste, and overlay slot drawings on top of it using HTML Canvas.

> [!NOTE]
> **Slot Detection**: Full AI-based slot detection (using computer vision) requires a Python ML backend. For this version, slot status will be managed via:
> 1. Admin manually marks slots occupied/empty
> 2. Pre-booked slots auto-marked as "reserved"
> 3. Future: ML service integration point is provided

